# Core packages for Arch Linux.
# Installed via `make -C os/arch install-packages-core` (runs pacman).
#
# See docs/environment/README.md in tamakiii/myfiles for rationale and the
# distinction between built-in Claude Code tools and shell-invoked ones.
#
# Format: one package per line. Blank lines and '#' comments are ignored.

